text: Lena Krier (born 29 March 1994) is a Luxembourger footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Dames Ligue 1 club SC Bettembourg and the Luxembourg women's national team. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Luxembourgian women's footballers Category:Luxembourg women's international footballers
